data.description: Welcome to this charming three-bedroom, two-bath home that is an entertainers dream. Enjoy the spacious open areas, as you walk in you will find yourself relaxing in your precious new home. The living room boasts built-in surround sound speakers, perfect for hosting movie nights or relaxing to your favorite tunes. Enjoy entertaining outdoors in your backyard surrounded by a privacy fence all around which also backs up into a green belt. Home is conveniently located near SW Loop 410/281, SW Military Dr., Brooks City Base and Missions all nearby. Texas A&M and Palo Alto College only minutes away. So many entertainment and dining venues to chose from. DON'T MISS OUT on this 2018 jewel!!
